    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "5c38db68-a931-40b5-a29f-6f8c4eddeaa0",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showVignette",
                    "vignetteName": "FirstAidClassIndoor.png",
                    "crossFadeTime": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "77412153-62c3-43ef-a175-57dd895da630",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f8b27c95-98a1-4237-ad7c-1edf929a1898",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we will be discussing the Fairy Parasol. This is often found growing in Faerie rings or other magical areas. It resembles an iridescent, slightly luminous parasol.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "229a9527-0c9c-46a0-99b7-72ebd5e5d49c",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It is highly magical and has a wide range of uses in potions. Eaten raw, it enhances a person's natural magical abilities.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e5e5b7b9-ccd9-43d9-9781-6aa483d3068d",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Now many of you do not have any noticeable magical traits. However, everyone has some latent skill for magic, even if it is indetectable. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "29ab5fce-17f8-4bf3-b54a-4289af4964ae",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Eating a Fairy Parasol will not give you the ability to cast spells or become a Wizard. It will, of course, increase your magical skills if you do use magic.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e9a39338-8ac3-4933-9b53-d37af4b897f3",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "What eating the Fairy Parasol will do for all of you is increase your natural resistance to hostile magic directed at you. This will shield you from some of the magical damage from a Revenant's spell, for instance.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "fcf638f5-29cf-494b-8e9b-c100af02413e",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "cd5b9b21-ecdd-484f-a2e4-e810d0e04646",
                            "text": "Say Something Heroic and Inspiring",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fbc49a80-a0ef-4f08-b447-2785eab1463d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "If we eat a Fairy Parasol, does that mean we can fight an evil Wraith? That seems like a heroic thing we all should aspire to do.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "03583f0e-5e27-431c-82d7-82a175798f5e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "36",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "7c24b87c-3ec1-4ec5-b480-3b75a85b1858",
                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9eb1b2de-d415-4f95-98fe-666544d62786",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "None of you should face a Wraith until after you graduate from this university. Wraiths are very powerful and extremely dangerous. Eating a Fairy Parasol may help you run away from a Wraith, but it will not prevent the Wraith from destroying you if you try to fight it.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "fe77db29-ece6-4a7a-9d01-b8f00f077ca4",
                            "text": "Say Something Intelligent About Faerie Parasols",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "056ad759-5f8c-4ebd-b9b5-8e2f5786e554",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "If Fairy Parasols grow in Faerie rings, doesn't that make it dangerous to pick them? I mean, won't the Faeries object?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "3bcf902e-81d6-4c72-b68e-e8c43b9a99c8",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "36",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "b0ad89fd-f6c9-4631-8edc-d58aca506f28",
                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a664c43a-4e3d-4989-b580-bc210b0d981a",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, you should never pick mushrooms from a Faerie ring without the permission of the Faeries. However, you can safely pick them whenever you find them growing in a clump in woods or a cave.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "88c2a2b9-2ea6-481b-8771-7da821c68d33",
                            "text": "Say Something Humorous",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b29ba766-1a82-4dbb-be9a-59dfb984eeb1",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Do you need a Faerie ring to get engaged to a Pixie, or are you just better off wed?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
